# Public images need only the files copied by Dockerfile. Keep every other
# workspace file—including local data, credentials, logs, media, test captures,
# release keys, and client build artifacts—out of the build context entirely.
*
!Dockerfile
!.dockerignore
!package.json
!LICENSE
!THIRD-PARTY-NOTICES.md
!server/
!server/**
!web/
!web/**
!docker/
!docker/entrypoint.sh
